OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1772741478
OL,3,CHeadteacher suspended under
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FThe headteacher of Sark's only school
OL,7,Fhas been suspended and is under
OL,8,Finvestigation by her employer.
OL,10,FMichelle Brady moved to the island in
OL,11,FSeptember 2022, having previously
OL,12,Fworked in education settings across
OL,13,FGuernsey and the UK.
OL,15,FThe official reason behind her
OL,16,Fsuspension, which was actioned by her
OL,17,Femployer, the Sark Chief Pleas'
OL,18,FEducation Committee, on Friday (27
OL,19,FFebruary) has not been disclosed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1772741478
OL,3,CHeadteacher suspended under
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FThe decision was made two days after
OL,7,FMs Brady's son, Jacob Brady, 23, was
OL,8,Fsentenced to more than four years in
OL,9,Fprison for the sexual touching of a
OL,10,Fteenage girl and possessing indecent
OL,11,Fimages of children.
OL,13,FIt has been confirmed that Jacob
OL,14,FBrady's offences are not related to
OL,15,FSark or Sark School.
OL,17,FIt has also been confirmed that
OL,18,FMichelle Brady was not and is not
OL,19,Funder any criminal investigation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1772741478
OL,3,CHeadteacher suspended under
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FChief Pleas has confirmed that Simon
OL,7,FSmith, the school's Safeguarding Lead
OL,8,Fand Head of Maths, Science and Music,
OL,9,Fwill serve as its interim headteacher.
OL,11,FRhys Rowlands, Senior Operations
OL,12,FOfficer at Chief Pleas, added: "As an
OL,13,Finvestigation is ongoing, it would not
OL,14,Fbe appropriate to comment further at
OL,15,Fthis time, save to note that temporary
OL,16,Fsuspension while an investigation is
OL,17,Fundertaken is standard practice and
OL,18,Fdoes not imply a finding of
OL,19,Fwrongdoing."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
