OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1772741478
OL,3,CHeadteacher suspended under
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FJan Guy, Chair of the Board of
OL,7,FGovernors at Sark School, confirmed
OL,8,Fthe decision to place Ms Brady on
OL,9,Fleave was not made by them, but added
OL,10,Fthey "cannot make any comment while
OL,11,Fthe suspension enquiry is being
OL,12,Fcarried out".
OL,14,FSark's education system operates
OL,15,Findependently from Guernsey, with the
OL,16,Fschool offering mixed-age classes to
OL,17,Faround 30 students aged between three
OL,18,Fand 13.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
