CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1772741478
OL,3,CHeadteacher suspended under
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FOn Friday 27 February, a school
OL,7,Fnewsletter was distributed with Ms
OL,8,FBrady stating she was "looking
OL,9,Fforward" to the forthcoming school
OL,10,Fterm and the Guernsey Eisteddfod.
OL,12,FITV News has contacted Ms Brady for a
OL,13,Fresponse.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
